612952.detail_best:
Grants the user effects based on the number of their “Paint” types
1 or more: Damage dealt +<skl_ailment_value>% and
enables critical hits with elemental attacks
3 or more: Also, Elem. Atk +<skl_ailment_value2>% and
raises the cap on Elem. Atk Up from support skills and equipment to <skl_ailment_value3>%
6 or more: Also, adds <skl_ailment_value4>% of your P.Atk to your Elem. Atk
(including equipment stats/Uses the highest value for each stat)

612942.detail_best:
After you act (only actions in turn order/Triggers only once regardless of action),
if you have a specific color combination of “Paint,”
grants all allies in the front row and back row the corresponding special effect “Paint.”
“Red” + “Blue”: Grants the special effect “Paint: Purple”
(3 turns/Granted as a battle ability)
“Red” + “Yellow”: Grants the special effect “Paint: Orange”
(3 turns/Granted as a battle ability)
“Blue” + “Yellow”: Grants the special effect “Paint: Green”
(3 turns/Granted as a battle ability)<sidenote>
Paint: When using an elemental attack other than “Attack” (some excluded),
you can exploit the weakness corresponding to the color.
(Damage is calculated according to each attack)
Red: Fire, Blue: Ice, Yellow: Lightning, Green: Wind, Orange: Light, Purple: Dark
If the duration reaches 9 turns or more, it will no longer expire as turns pass
